      >
        <p>
          &quot;Amazing agency to work for, the team is amazing and always produce top quality work&quot;
        </p>
      </blockquote>
      <figcaption class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-x-6">
				<Image src={amThumbnail} alt="" class="size-12 rounded-full bg-gray-50" />
        <div class="text-sm/6">
          <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Andrew McInnes</div>
